#

Lemon and Sugar Crepes

25 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

French

Course:

Dessert

Tags:

DessertBreakfastEasy

Description

Delicately thin crepes drizzled with fresh lemon juice and sprinkled with sugar for a sweet and tangy treat.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • milk: 1 cup
  • eggs: 2
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon zest: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: a pinch
